PrecisAuthority for the AGRICULTURAL PRODUCTS BOARD to purchase, store, transport or process up to 650 metric tonnes of surplus grapes grown in the Province of Ontario during 1990, or to enter into contracts with third parties in connection therewith, and to incur a financial loss upon their resale.
